re process the image file to orient the tissue per the orientation markers / orientation ink drawn at necropsy
Identify the ROI and analyze in Visiopharm
The output TSV files are fed used to analyze
The script generates an Excel file that has two tabs - one tab has the raw original data and the second tab has the Processed data. 
Operations carried out by the script:
1. shift of the nerve bundles x,y co-ordinates relative to the lumen x.y co -ordinates i.e. shift of origin operation
2. calculation of the relative angle using the ATAN2 fx 
3.binning the nerves using the values from #2 into 4 anatomical quadrants (=IF(AND(M2>=45,M2<135),"Quadrant 1",IF(AND(M2>=135,M2<225),"Quadrant 4",IF(AND(M2>=225,M2<315),"Quadrant 3","Quadrant 2"))))
5. counting nerves per quadrant
